erna — 3x12 (cierre y estiramiento)\\\\n\\\\nNotas:\\\\n- Descansa 2-3 min entre series pesadas, 90 seg en auxiliares.\\\\n- Si llegas fresco, arranca fuerte en banca; si hay fatiga, baja un 10% de carga.\\\\n- Calienta: 5 min movilidad de hombros + 2 series de calentamiento.\\\\n- Son las 5AM — hidratación antes de arrancar.\\\\n\\\\nTodo listo para las 5. ¡A darle! ⚔️\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nAca me diste la rutina @75806961324068  seria que la ajustaras a torso (pecho y espalda) sabes la rutina que tenemos definida ?\"}],\"timestamp\":1774553716762}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"4d343243\",\"parentId\":\"0167c87d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-26T19:35:26.869Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[],\"api\":\"openai-codex-responses\",\"provider\":\"openai-codex\",\"model\":\"gpt-5.4\",\"usage\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"totalTokens\":0,\"cost\":{\"input\":0,\"output\":0,\"cacheRead\":0,\"cacheWrite\":0,\"total\":0}},\"stopReason\":\"error\",\"timestamp\":1774553716765,\"errorMessage\":\"You have hit your ChatGPT usage limit (plus plan). Try again in ~6182 min.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"custom\",\"customType\":\"model-snapshot\",\"data\":{\"timestamp\":1774553727358,\"provider\":\"anthropic\",\"modelApi\":\"anthropic-messages\",\"modelId\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\"},\"id\":\"f3c55ea3\",\"parentId\":\"4d343243\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-26T19:35:27.358Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"4beb2e37\",\"parentId\":\"f3c55ea3\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-26T19:35:27.367Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"message_id\\\": \\\"3AC1FC8C30889DB0B031\\\",\\n  \\\"reply_to_id\\\": \\\"3EB0515864DF20C043912C\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"205157820289127@lid\\\",\\n  \\\"conversation_label\\\": \\\"120363424964463765@g.us\\\",\\n  \\\"sender\\\": \\\"Gustavo Toledo\\\",\\n  \\\"group_subject\\\": \\\"Smart project\\\",\\n  \\\"is_group_chat\\\": true,