{"type":"message","id":"0bf6a6f8","parentId":"39d973bb","timestamp":"2026-03-27T18:45:07.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No hay Haiku configurado en esta instalación. El ajuste más barato y estable disponible sin tocar credenciales nuevas es **GPT**. Voy a dejar a Ares en GPT-5.4 y sacar el 30B del routing.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b5379d175373a9a0169c6d02f23a0819195591340ba1e0d46\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_U2ZLskonDtWmcQDKODNe5gQ7|fc_0b5379d175373a9a0169c6d0300acc8191b45ef811623f3d20","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","old_string":"                                {\n                                    \"id\":  \"ares\",\n                                    \"name\":  \"ares\",\n                                    \"workspace\":  \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace-ares\",\n                                    \"agentDir\":  \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\ares\\\\agent\",\n                                    \"groupChat\":  {\n                                                      \"mentionPatterns\":  [\n                                                                              \"\\\\bares\\\\b\",\n                                                                              \"\\\\bAres\\\\b\"\n                                                                          ],\n                                                      \"historyLimit\":  50\n                                                  },\n                                    \"model\":  {\n                                                  \"primary\":  \"ollama/qwen3:30b\",\n                                                  \"fallbacks\":  [\n                                                                    \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n                                                                    \"openai-codex/gpt-5.4\"